  "title": "Staff Nurse (Office Hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description: </strong><br />We are seeking a detail-oriented and organized Registered Nurse to support daily operations at our healthcare clinic. The role involves performing general nursing duties, coordinating patient care, and ensuring efficient clinic operations. <br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities: </strong><br />•\tGeneral nursing duties in clinic which include preparing patients for their health screening or radiology services <br />•\tAble to perform cannulation <br />•\tTo assist doctor during consultation or in any procedures / treatment <br />•\tHandle any registration, appointment bookings and answer any phone call enquiries <br />•\tFollow up with patients on any feedback / concerns that they may have <br />•\tInteract and coordinate with different teams to ensure that the centre's operations is running smoothly and efficiently <br />•\tMaintain the cleanliness and readiness of all equipment / instruments <br />•\tAssist in collating patients' medical results and documents any patient assessment findings and progress •\tManaging nursing consumable, medication & E-cart <br />•\tAssist in Theragnostic cases •\tCross cover Imaging and Wellness department whenever needed <br />•\tProvide administrative support to the department when required <br />•\tAny other adhoc duties as assigned by the reporting managers <br /><br /><strong>Requirements: </strong><br />•\t2 years related experience <br />•\tSingapore Nursing Board Practising Certificate is a MUST <br />•\tStrong team player <br />•\t5.5 days work week (Monday to Friday; Saturday - half day) <br />•\tLocation: Buona Vista/Orchard</p>",
